OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773835370
OL,3,CBakery fined thousands after worker
OL,4,Cinjured themselves on premises
OL,6,FA bakery company has been fined
OL,7,Fthousands of pounds after an employee
OL,8,Ffractured their hip while working.
OL,10,FThe incident occurred after the worker
OL,11,Ffell from a large plastic pallet box
OL,12,Fwhile "working at height" at
OL,13,FGreenhalgh's Craft Bakery Limited's
OL,14,Fsite in Lostock, Bolton on 15 April
OL,15,F2024.
OL,17,FAn investigation found they had been
OL,18,Fstanding on a pallet box to dispose of
OL,19,Ffood waste into the top of a skip when
OL,20,Fthey fell.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
