PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773835370
OL,3,CBakery fined thousands after worker
OL,4,Cinjured themselves on premises
OL,6,FA Health and Safety Executive (HSE)
OL,7,Finvestigation found that Greenhalgh's
OL,8,Fhad failed to carry out a suitable and
OL,9,Fsufficient risk assessment for loading
OL,10,Fskips and had not provided appropriate
OL,11,Fequipment to ensure safe access.
OL,13,FThe investigation also found that
OL,14,Fthere was "inadequate supervision and
OL,15,Fmonitoring" which had allowed unsafe
OL,16,Fworking at height practices to become
OL,17,Fcommonplace.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
