OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773835370
OL,3,CBakery fined thousands after worker
OL,4,Cinjured themselves on premises
OL,6,FGreenhalgh's Craft Bakery Limited, of
OL,7,FCrescent Road, Bolton, pleaded guilty
OL,8,Fto breaching Section 2 (1) of the
OL,9,FHealth and Safety at Work etc. Act
OL,10,F1974.
OL,12,FThe act states it is the duty of every
OL,13,Femployer to "ensure, so far as is
OL,14,Freasonably practicable, the health,
OL,15,Fsafety and welfare at work of all his
OL,16,Femployees".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773835370
OL,3,CBakery fined thousands after worker
OL,4,Cinjured themselves on premises
OL,6,FFollowing the guilty plea, the company
OL,7,Fwas fined #16,667 and was ordered to
OL,8,Fpay costs of #4,333.66, plus a victim
OL,9,Fsurcharge of #2,000 at Tameside
OL,10,FMagistrates' Court on 13 March.
OL,12,FThe company are speciality wholesale
OL,13,Fbakers who supply pies, bread,
OL,14,Fsavouries, sandwiches and a range of
OL,15,Fcelebration cakes nationwide.
OL,17,FAccording to HSE, working at height
OL,18,Fcontinues to remain one of the leading
OL,19,Fcauses of workplace injury and death.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
