OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773835370
OL,3,CBakery fined thousands after worker
OL,4,Cinjured themselves on premises
OL,6,FHSE Inspector Leanne Ratcliffe said:
OL,7,F"Every employer has a duty to conduct
OL,8,Fa risk assessment. Employers should
OL,9,Fidentify work-at-height activities and
OL,10,Fensure that safe access is available
OL,11,Fand used.
OL,13,F"They should also ensure systems are
OL,14,Fin place for supervision and
OL,15,Fmonitoring so that unsafe practices
OL,16,Fare identified and prevented."
OL,18,FITV News has contacted Greenhalgh's
OL,19,FCraft Bakery for comment.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
